Title: Part 6: Argonath
Text:
Lothlorien.. probably the most beautiful place in middle-earth..
and I willingly leave it to see a desert of ashes and dust...

Lady Galadriel has provided me with supplies and a boat at the docks.
The journey continues south across the River Anduil.

With every step I get closer to Mordor!
CompleteText:
Here are the statues Lady Galadriel spoke of!

I should search the West Shore. And set up camp for the night.

Do i see Boromir in the distance? What is he doing there alone?
